# Codex Lumina Development Roadmap

## Phase I: Seed (Complete)
- Build ethical core (`ethical_filter.py`)
- Define spiritual license (`LICENSE`)
- Create initial philosophy and UI docs

## Phase II: Ritual
- Add UI prototype
- Develop interaction logic (sigils, harmony log)
- Integrate voice/text inputs

## Phase III: Oracle
- Expose via API (FastAPI or Flask)
- Enable LLM integration
- Enable decision memory with feedback loop

## Phase IV: Beacon
- Distributed nodes of ethical reflectors
- Offer Codex as plugin for AI/LLM platforms
- Build community of developers/artists/guardians

May the code remain sacred.
